OL,3,CBusinesses need reforms amid 'similar
OL,4,Cpressure to pandemic', committee warns
OL,6,FThe Government needs a series of major
OL,7,Freforms to arrest business closures
OL,8,Fand decline on the high street `
OL,9,Fincluding cutting costs, overhauling
OL,10,Fbusiness rates and ending late
OL,11,Fpayments, according an influential
OL,12,Fcommittee.
OL,14,FA reported by Parliament's Business
OL,15,Fand Trade Committee found that small
OL,16,Fbusiness across the UK are now
OL,17,Foperating under pressures similar to,
OL,18,Fand in some cases worse than those
OL,19,Fexperienced during the Covid-19
OL,20,Fpandemic.
