OL,3,CBusinesses need reforms amid 'similar
OL,4,Cpressure to pandemic', committee warns
OL,6,FLiam Byrne, chair of the committee,
OL,7,Fsaid a "more coherent and ambitious
OL,8,Fplan" is needed to support businesses.
OL,10,FThe fresh report by the committee
OL,11,Ffound that current pressure are
OL,12,F"cumulative, structural and self-
OL,13,Freinforcing".
OL,15,FIt added that the level of current
OL,16,Fpressures mean there is a risk of
OL,17,Faccelerating business closures and the
OL,18,FGovernment undermining its growth
OL,19,Fagenda without action.
