OL,3,CBusinesses need reforms amid 'similar
OL,4,Cpressure to pandemic', committee warns
OL,6,FIt highlighted late payments as a
OL,7,Fspecific issue which needs attention,
OL,8,Fpointing towards evidence from Sage
OL,9,Findicating that UK small businesses
OL,10,Fwere owed #112 billion in unpaid
OL,11,Finvoices by the end of 2024.
OL,13,FNearly half of all invoices are paid
OL,14,Flate, even with payment terms of 60 to
OL,15,F90 days now routine in sectors such as
OL,16,Fconstruction, it added.
