OL,3,CBusinesses need reforms amid 'similar
OL,4,Cpressure to pandemic', committee warns
OL,6,FThe report also drew attention to a
OL,7,Fpattern of closures on UK high
OL,8,Fstreets, after the committee heard
OL,9,Fevidence that business rates, retail
OL,10,Fcrime and energy costs are
OL,11,Fdisproportionately affecting bricks-
OL,12,Fand-mortar businesses.
OL,14,FMr Byrne said: "SMEs are facing late
OL,15,Fpayments, rising energy costs,
OL,16,Fincreasing crime, a complex tax system
OL,17,Fand barriers to growth that are
OL,18,Fcompounding rather than easing.
