OL,3,CBusinesses need reforms amid 'similar
OL,4,Cpressure to pandemic', committee warns
OL,6,F"These pressures are not isolated;
OL,7,Ftogether they pose a real risk to
OL,8,Fbusiness viability, high streets and
OL,9,Feconomic growth.
OL,11,F"High streets do not die by accident.
OL,13,F"If the Government is serious about
OL,14,Fgrowth, it must set out a more
OL,15,Fcoherent and ambitious plan for the
OL,16,Fbusinesses that make up so much of the
OL,17,FUK economy."
