OL,3,CBusinesses need reforms amid 'similar
OL,4,Cpressure to pandemic', committee warns
OL,6,FA Government spokesperson said: "Small
OL,7,Fbusinesses are the lifeblood of our
OL,8,Fcommunities and while we know they are
OL,9,Ffacing a difficult time, we are
OL,10,Fdetermined to make the UK the best
OL,11,Fplace for them to thrive.
OL,13,F"That's why we are supporting them
OL,14,Fwith a #4.3 billion support package to
OL,15,Fcap big business rate bill hikes and
OL,16,Fby taking action through our Modern
OL,17,FIndustrial Strategy and Small Business
OL,18,FPlan, and we will also publish a new
OL,19,FHigh Streets Strategy later this year
OL,20,Fto reinvigorate our communities."
