OL,3,CBusinesses need reforms amid 'similar
OL,4,Cpressure to pandemic', committee warns
OL,6,FShadow business secretary Andrew
OL,7,FGriffith said: "Today's report from
OL,8,Fthe Business and Trade Select
OL,9,FCommittee confirms what high street
OL,10,Fbusinesses already know: business
OL,11,Frates, retail crime and energy costs
OL,12,Fare pushing bricks and mortar shops to
OL,13,Fthe brink.
OL,15,F"Labour's answer is higher taxes and
OL,16,Fmore regulation."
